  "title": "Padding in Pagination stops working after update  2.3->2.6.3",
  "body": "I have 2 pagination widgets on site. \r\n\r\n```\r\nsearch.addWidget(instantsearch.widgets.pagination({\r\n    padding: 2, \r\n    container: '#pagination',\r\n    scrollTo: '.pw_st_search_search'\r\n  }));\r\n  search.addWidget(instantsearch.widgets.pagination({\r\n    padding: 4,\r\n    container: '#pagination_bottom',\r\n    scrollTo: '.pw_st_search_search'\r\n  }));\r\n```\r\nEverything works well with instantsearch 2.3, but after update to 2.6.3 i got 3 padding on both widgets and cant change it. Is it bug? \r\n\r\n",
